(492, 'Emanuele Pavarotti', 'emanuele-pavarotti', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/emanuele-pavarotti.jpg', '<p>I\'m an Italian painter and animator based in NY. Over the past 8 years I worked as a character animator with Disney - Blue Sky Studios. Currently I\'m working with Netflix as a visual development artist.</p>\r\n<p>My paintings depict everyday, ordinary scenes with a whimsical twist.</p>\r\n<p>My visual language is influenced by \'90s video games and anime that I used to love when I was a kid.</p>', 'https://twitter.com/calcif3r', 'http://emanuelepavarotti.com/', 'emanuele.pavarotti@gmail.com', '', '0', '1620970245', NULL, 'https://www.instagram.com/calcif3r/'),
