(156, 'Build an Art Gallery in Minecraft', 'build-an-art-gallery-in-minecraft', '2020-12-20', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/build-an-art-gallery-in-minecraft.png', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Sunday, Dec 20, 2020, 9:00am PT (2 hours) (check your <a href=\"https://time.is/0900AM_20_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Part of the&nbsp;<strong>10th</strong> annual <a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\">Build your own virtual art gallery in Minecraft with Hufo. This is a workshop for all ages! No need to be a coder or a Minecraft expert, in this workshop Hufo will give you all the help you need to grasp some Minecraft foundations and basic commands and build your own virtual art gallery on Minecraft.</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- TicketTailor BUTTON (start) ----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/460517#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a> to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT </strong></em><em>for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<!-- TicketTailor BUTTON (end) ----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž SKILL LEVEL ã€</h3>\r\n<p>Open to all levels and ages. No specific background required for this workshop, just bring your curiosity!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž WORKSHOP OUTLINE ã€</h3>\r\n<p>This is a 2 hour workshop includes:</p>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li>Introduction to&nbsp;Minecraft</li>\r\n<li>Visit the CODAME Minecraft Art Gallery together</li>\r\n<li>Exercise:&nbsp;Building gallery structure</li>\r\n<li>Exercise:&nbsp;Uploading your art</li>\r\n<li>Break out rooms: build your own galley or&nbsp;as a team</li>\r\n<li>Show your gallery to the attendees</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž REQUIREMENTS ã€</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Install Minecraft (Java Edition) on your computer (<a href=\"https://www.minecraft.net/store/minecraft-java-edition\">link</a>)</li>\r\n<li>Java Edition Minecraft account (you will be asked the username&nbsp;during&nbsp;ticket registration or workshop)</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">And the usual:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">\r\n<li>Computer &amp; power/charger.</li>\r\n<li>Zoom installed (<a href=\"https://zoom.us/download\">download</a>)</li>\r\n<li>Optional: 2nd monitor or screen so you can see the Zoom while working</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<iframe style=\"background-image: url(\'/admin/img/object.gif\');\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/D8N1pUr7tx8\" width=\"780\" height=\"439\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://www.eventbrite.com/custombutton?eid=34741461647\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Workshops\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /> Get tickets now to reserve your spot for <br />an extraordinary learning experience. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: bold; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/build-a-virtual-art-gallery-in-minecraft1.png\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/2020-11-28_08.40_.44_.png\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"/uploaded_images/2020-11-28_08.54_.08_.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/2020-11-28_08.52_.06_.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">This workshop is part of the&nbsp;10th&nbsp;annual&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž CODAME&nbsp;#CodeArtTogether Workshops ã€</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 101px;\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸ§ âœ¨</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Connect</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-81f37ba5-7fff-97be-c713-6edc787897a0\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸš§ðŸŽ¨</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Create</span></span></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸ¤©ðŸ’¬ </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Celebrate</span></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Connecting, Creating, and Celebrating&nbsp;are pillars of the&nbsp;<a href=\"/projects/code-art-together\">CODAME #CodeArtTogether workshops</a>!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Workshops are great for team building, remote or IRL. They cultivate space to play, which guides sense-making and sparks innovation. Attendees become featured artists with the option to show their workshop creations in CODAME galleries.&nbsp;<a href=\"/projects/code-art-together\">Learn more about this exciting offering</a><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/checkout/view-event/id/486392/chk/4cfa/?modal_widget=true&amp;widget=true&amp;d\">!</a></p>\r\n<p>What topics grab your curiosity to learn or teach?&nbsp;Let us know through our&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/call-for-workshops\">call for workshops</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/join-us\">#JOYNT US</a>&nbsp;as a sponsor, volunteer, or workshop leader!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 101px;\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/460517#ticket_selection\"><br /><br /><br /><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://www.eventbrite.com/custombutton?eid=34741461647\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Workshops\" /></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Join us</h2>\r\n<center>\r\n<p><a href=\"/pages/join-us\">Join us</a>. Sponsor, Volunteer or lead a workshop.&nbsp;<br />What topics grab your curiosity to learn or teach?&nbsp;<br />Let us know through our&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/call-for-workshops\">call for workshops</a>.</p>\r\n</center><center>ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</center>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">CODAME is a member of Intersection for the Arts&nbsp;<br />a non profit 501(c)(3)&nbsp;organization.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">All proceeds will be split with the participating artists.&nbsp;<br /><a href=\"https://www.flipcause.com/secure/cause_pdetails/NjU0OA==\">Donations</a>&nbsp;are always welcome.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thank you for your support for ART &hearts;ï¸ TECH !!!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/pages/code-of-conduct\">Code of Conduct</a>&nbsp;for all attendees.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'hufo', 'minecraft-art-tech-gallery,minecraft-gallery-shaders', '', '', '', '', '0', 'workshop', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/460517#ticket_selection', ''),
(165, 'Harddiskmuseum Tour', 'harddiskmuseum-tour', '2020-12-14', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/harddiskmuseum-tour.png', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Part of the 10th annual <a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a> (included in the</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a>&nbsp;)</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Monday, Dec 14, 2020, 10:00am PST (check your&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The Harddiskmuseum is a Museum of digital and new media art content based in a hard drive of 2TB founded by the artist Solim&aacute;n L&oacute;pez in 2015.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Now in 2020 the Museum includes the pieces of 110 artists from more than 20 different countries. Artworks of video, static images, video games, text, audio pieces, interactive pieces and a long etc.. are part of this unique repository.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>At the end of 2020 the Museum will have its version in genetic code. The first Museum in history to store its content in DNA.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Workshops\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'soliman-lopez', '', '', 'd2d-art', '', '', '0', 'event', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection', 'art-tech-festival-2020-joynt'),
(160, 'modV Audio Visual Live Performance ', 'modv-audio-visual-live-performance', '2020-12-13', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/modv-audio-visual-live-performance.png', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Part of the 10th annual <a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a> (included in the</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a>&nbsp;)</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Sunday, Dec 13, 2020, 11:30am PST (check your&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Sam (aka 2xAA) and Tim (aka NERDDISCO) are working on the open source visuals software called modV to use the power of the web to bring fine visuals to everyone. When they are doing a live performance, 2xAA is doing music using his Game Boys and NERDDISCO is using some shaders from Shadertoy in modV to generate visuals based on the music from 2xAA. They want to show that everyone can use modV for their shows.<span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.3333px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Workshops\" /></a></p>', 'tim-pietrusky,sam-wray', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 'event', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection', 'art-tech-festival-2020-joynt'),
(181, '3D Graphics and Animation with Shader Park', '3d-graphics-and-animation-with-shader-park', '2020-12-17', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/3d-graphics-and-animation-with-shader-park.png', '<center>Thursday, December 17th @ 3:00PM PST (<a href=\"https://time.is/3PM_17_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\" target=\"_blank\">timezone converter</a>)</center>\r\n<p><!-- Ticket Tailor Widget. Paste this in to your website where you want the widget to appear. Do no change the code or the widget may not work properly. --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<p id=\"&rdquo;fest-10&rdquo;\"><em>Part of the&nbsp;<strong>10th</strong> annual <a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</center>\r\n<h3>Explore 3D shader programming through a Javascript interface without the complexity of GLSL. Shader Park is an open source project for creating real-time graphics and procedural animations. Follow along through multiple examples using a P5.js style live code editor. Expand upon the examples to create your own interactive 3D graphics. Explore the Shader Park community gallery where you can fork other people\'s creations or feature your own!</h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- TicketTailor BUTTON (start) ----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/461015#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a> to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT </strong></em><em>for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<!-- TicketTailor BUTTON (end) ----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>In computational design, &ldquo;The real challenge is to discover the intrinsic properties of the new medium and to find out how the stroke you draw via computation is one you could never draw, or even imagine without computation&rdquo; (John Maeda: Design by Numbers).\"&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž SKILL LEVEL ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Beginner. No Coding required.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž WORKSHOP OUTLINE ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Introduction to Shader Park</li>\r\n<li>Break-out Group for Exploration</li>\r\n<li>Over-view of basic functions and interfaces within Shader Park</li>\r\n<li>Tutorial on building objects with Geometry</li>\r\n<li>Building a 3d mug, with break-out groups</li>\r\n<li>Exploration of more advanced features such as color and modulation</li>\r\n<li>Final break-out room to explore what you\'ve learned</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž ATTENDES BRING ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Quickly create&nbsp;an account with <a href=\"https://shaderpark.netlify.app/\">Shader Park</a> (you will have time during to workshop to do this as well)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>And the usual:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Computer &amp; power/charger.</li>\r\n<li>Zoom installed ahead of time.</li>\r\n<li>Optional: 2nd monitor or screen so you can see the Zoom while working.</li>\r\n<li>Hop on the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/pk3C8DB\">CODAME Discord</a>&nbsp;if you have questions!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž SCHEDULE ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Thu, Dec 17</li>\r\n<li>3PM PT - 5PM PT</li>\r\n<li>2.5 hours</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p><iframe src=\"https://shaderpark.netlify.com/embed/-MOnQxnhZCJV4iXXpnZ_\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></p>\r\n<!-- TicketTailor BUTTON (start) ----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/461015#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a> to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT </strong></em><em>for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<!-- TicketTailor BUTTON (end) ----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: left;\">ã€Ž CODAME&nbsp;#CodeArtTogether Workshops ã€</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 101px;\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸ§ âœ¨</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Connect</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-81f37ba5-7fff-97be-c713-6edc787897a0\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸš§ðŸŽ¨</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Create</span></span></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸ¤©ðŸ’¬ </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Celebrate</span></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start;\">Connecting, Creating, and Celebrating&nbsp;are pillars of the&nbsp;<a href=\"/projects/code-art-together\">CODAME #CodeArtTogether workshops</a>!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start;\">Workshops are great for team building, remote or IRL. They cultivate space to play, which guides sense-making and sparks innovation. Attendees become featured artists with the option to show their workshop creations in CODAME galleries.&nbsp;<a href=\"/projects/code-art-together\">Learn more about this exciting offering</a><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/checkout/view-event/id/486392/chk/4cfa/?modal_widget=true&amp;widget=true&amp;d\">!</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start;\">What topics grab your curiosity to learn or teach?&nbsp;Let us know through our&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/call-for-workshops\">call for workshops</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/join-us\">#JOYNT US</a>&nbsp;as a sponsor, volunteer, or workshop leader!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: start;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center>ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</center>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">CODAME is a member of Intersection for the Arts&nbsp;<br />a non profit 501(c)(3)&nbsp;organization.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">All proceeds will be split with the participating artists.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.flipcause.com/secure/cause_pdetails/NjU0OA==\">Donations</a>&nbsp;are always welcome.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thank you for your support for ART &hearts;ï¸ TECH !!!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/pages/code-of-conduct\">Code of Conduct</a>&nbsp;for all attendees.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'torin-blankensmith,peter-whidden', 'art-tech-festival-2020-joynt', '', '', '', '', '0', 'workshop', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/461015#ticket_selection', ''),
(171, 'Mint Crypto Art Tokens', 'mint-crypto-art-tokens', '2020-12-11', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/mint-crypto-art-tokens.png', '<center>Friday, December 11th @ 11:30AM PST (<a href=\"https://time.is/11:30AM_11_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\" target=\"_blank\">timezone converter</a>)</center>\r\n<p><!-- Ticket Tailor Widget. Paste this in to your website where you want the widget to appear. Do no change the code or the widget may not work properly. --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------></p>\r\n<center>\r\n<p id=\"&rdquo;fest-10&rdquo;\"><em>Part of the&nbsp;<strong>10th</strong> annual <a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</center>\r\n<h3>Make your mark on the Ethereum blockchain by minting your art as a crypto collectable! Before getting there we\'ll cover the fundementals of crypto art with Q&amp;A time to take the edge off the overwhelming terminology and concepts. The crypto art scene is an vibrant source of inspiration. Join the super connector ride where new light is being shed on the value of creativity... whether you\'re a traditional artist, animator, photographer, or other!&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-- TicketTailor BUTTON (start) ----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/463070#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a> to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT </strong></em><em>for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<!-- TicketTailor BUTTON (end) ----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž SKILL LEVEL ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Beginner. No Coding required.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž WORKSHOP OUTLINE ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>TBA</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž ATTENDES BRING ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Create a wallet ahead of time.</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"https://metamask.io/\">Metamask</a>&nbsp;is a popular option for getting started (<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xj14_XnaAIk\" target=\"_blank\">explainer video</a>).&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>You will need to let us know your wallet address (starts with 0x)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Bring some art you want to mint on the blockchain.</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>This could be an image, mp3, mp4 video, or even a 3d GLTF.&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Write a title and description for your artwork ahead of time.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<li>Hop on the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/pk3C8DB\">CODAME Discord</a>&nbsp;if you have questions!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>And the usual:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Computer &amp; power/charger.</li>\r\n<li>Zoom installed ahead of time.</li>\r\n<li>Optional: 2nd monitor or screen so you can see the Zoom while working.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž CODAME PROVIDES ã€</h3>\r\n<p>Slides TBA</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž SCHEDULE ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Fri, Dec 11</li>\r\n<li>11:30 AM PT - 2 PM PT (<a href=\"https://time.is/11:30AM_11_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\" target=\"_blank\">timezone.is</a>)</li>\r\n<li>2.5 hours</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<!-- TicketTailor BUTTON (start) ----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/463070#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a> to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT </strong></em><em>for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<!-- TicketTailor BUTTON (end) ----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/l1GvgujOO1M?start=29\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe style=\"display