e Arts&nbsp;<br />a non profit 501(c)(3)&nbsp;organization.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">All proceeds will be split with the participating artists.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.flipcause.com/secure/cause_pdetails/NjU0OA==\">Donations</a>&nbsp;are always welcome.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thank you for your support for ART &hearts;ï¸ TECH !!!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/pages/code-of-conduct\">Code of Conduct</a>&nbsp;for all attendees.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'william-bear-idressi', 'art-tech-festival-2020-joynt', '', 'opensea,cargo', '', '', '0', 'workshop', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/463070#ticket_selection', ''),
(161, 'Poetic Programming with in:verse', 'poetic-programming-with-in-verse', '2020-12-19', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/poetic-programming-with-in-verse.png', '<center>Saturday, December 19th @ 2:00pm PST (<a href=\"https://time.is/2:00PM_19_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\" target=\"_blank\">timezone converter</a>)</center><center>\r\n<p id=\"&rdquo;fest-10&rdquo;\"><em>Part of the&nbsp;<strong>10th</strong>&nbsp;annual&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></em></p>\r\n</center>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Create visuals and animations by writing poetry! in:verse is an esoteric programming language where code is written as poetry to generate shaders, in a live-coding web-based interface. This workshop will introduce participants to the fascinating world of esoteric programming languages, stack-based programming, shaders, and writing programs with in:verse. Participants can mold the language to their liking by choosing their own lexicon to program with, publish their work to an online gallery, and remix and build off each other\'s work.</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><!-- TicketTailor BUTTON (start) ----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------></p>\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/461143#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a> to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT </strong></em><em>for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><br /><br /><a href=\"https://inverse.website/#:~:text=in%3Averse%20is%20a%20programming,%2C%20visuals%2C%20mathematics%20and%20code.\">in:verse</a>&nbsp;follows a rich tradition of esoteric programming languages, challenging the core assumptions and values in mainstream programming languages. Rather than emphasize utility and efficiency, in:verse values playfulness, exploration and random chance. It allows one to engage with it on multiple levels -- focussing on either words and constraint-based writing; or on visuals and mathematical constraints; or bouncing between both.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž SCHEDULE ã€</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Sat,&nbsp;Dec 19th, 2020</li>\r\n<li class=\"graf graf--li\">2pmâ€Š&mdash;â€Š5:30pm PT (2.5 hours)&nbsp;<a class=\"markup--anchor markup--li-anchor\" href=\"/admin/ã€Ž SCHEDULE ã€\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-href=\"https://time.is/1100AM_18_October_2020_in_San_Francisco/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\">Check your timezone<br /><br /><br /><br /></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž SKILL LEVEL ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Basic familiarity with programming (in any language). Familiarity with shaders would be helpful but is not required.<br /><br /><br /><strong><u>Some Useful Prepatory Reading:</u></strong><u></u><br /><br />-&nbsp;<strong>An introduction to stack based programming:&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://skilldrick.github.io/easyforth\">https://skilldrick.github.io/easyforth</a>&nbsp;<br />(Only the sections \"<em>Adding some numbers\"</em> and \"<em>Stack Manipulation</em>\" are relevant)<br /><br />-&nbsp;<strong>The Book of Shaders:&nbsp;</strong><a href=\"https://thebookofshaders.com/01\">https://thebookofshaders.com/01</a><br />(up to the third section, or beyond!)<br />\r\n<div style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br /><br /></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž ATTENDES BRING ã€</h3>\r\n<p>The usual:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Computer &amp; power/charger.</li>\r\n<li>Zoom installed ahead of time.</li>\r\n<li>Optional: 2nd monitor or screen so you can see the Zoom while working.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž&nbsp;CODAME&nbsp;PROVIDES ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Instructor slides</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž CODAME&nbsp;#CodeArtTogether Workshops ã€</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 101px;\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸ§ âœ¨</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Connect</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-81f37ba5-7fff-97be-c713-6edc787897a0\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸš§ðŸŽ¨</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Create</span></span></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸ¤©ðŸ’¬ </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Celebrate</span></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Connecting, Creating, and Celebrating&nbsp;are pillars of the&nbsp;<a href=\"/projects/code-art-together\">CODAME #CodeArtTogether workshops</a>!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Workshops are great for team building, remote or IRL. They cultivate space to play, which guides sense-making and sparks innovation. Attendees become featured artists with the option to show their workshop creations in CODAME galleries.&nbsp;<a href=\"/projects/code-art-together\">Learn more about this exciting offering</a><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/checkout/view-event/id/486392/chk/4cfa/?modal_widget=true&amp;widget=true&amp;d\">!</a></p>\r\n<p>What topics grab your curiosity to learn or teach?&nbsp;Let us know through our&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/call-for-workshops\">call for workshops</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/join-us\">#JOYNT US</a>&nbsp;as a sponsor, volunteer, or workshop leader!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/461143#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a>&nbsp;to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT&nbsp;</strong></em><em>for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/uploaded_images/Screen_Shot_2020-12-11_at_10.46_.29_AM_.png\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/uploaded_images/Screen_Shot_2020-12-11_at_10.48_.04_AM_.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />&nbsp;<br /><img src=\"/uploaded_images/cover.png\" alt=\"\" /><br /><br /><img src=\"/uploaded_images/Screen_Shot_2020-12-11_at_10.49_.23_AM_1.png\" alt=\"\" /><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/uploaded_images/Screen_Shot_2020-12-11_at_10.49_.55_AM_1.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/uploaded_images/Screen_Shot_2020-12-11_at_10.50_.50_AM_.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/uploaded_images/Screen_Shot_2020-12-11_at_10.53_.35_AM_.png\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/uploaded_images/Screen_Shot_2020-12-11_at_10.51_.31_AM_.png\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center>ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</center>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">CODAME is a member of Intersection for the Arts&nbsp;<br />a non profit 501(c)(3)&nbsp;organization.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">All proceeds will be split with the participating artists.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.flipcause.com/secure/cause_pdetails/NjU0OA==\">Donations</a>&nbsp;are always welcome.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thank you for your support for ART &hearts;ï¸ TECH !!!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/pages/code-of-conduct\">Code of Conduct</a>&nbsp;for all attendees.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"tt-widget\">\r\n<div class=\"tt-widget-fallback\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<script src=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/js/widgets/min/widget.js\" type=\"mce-mce-no/type\" data-url=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/all-tickets/codame/ref/website_widget/\" data-type=\"inline\" data-inline-minimal=\"true\" data-inline-show-logo=\"false\" data-inline-bg-fill=\"true\"></script>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n|-- End Ticket Tailor Widget -----------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', 'sukanya-aneja', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 'workshop', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/461143#ticket_selection', '');
INSERT INTO `events` (`id`, `name`, `slug`, `date`, `pic`, `description`, `artists_array`, `projects_array`, `sponsors_array`, `partners_array`, `old_url`, `rsvp_url`, `hidden`, `event_type`, `shop_url`, `events_array`) VALUES
(162, 'Botanic Quartet', 'botanic-quartet', '2020-12-17', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/botanic-quartet.png', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Part of the 10th annual <a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a> (included in the</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a>&nbsp;)</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Thursday, Dec 17, 2020, 6:00pm PST (check your&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Botanic Quartet is a live performance of plants playing in a synchronized quartet with one another, and Scott Kildall improvising with a new DIY \"SnipSynth\" that he has developed on an ESP32 chip.<br /><br />For \"Botanic Quartet,\" each plant is hooked up to a sensor -- in most cases these are electrodes that read their rapidly-changing electrochemical activity. The data from this sensor gets processed by an embedded chip -- an ESP32 that plays the synthesized effects.<br /><br />For his performance, Scott is using records of San Francisco during SIP and will make the performance waiver on notes of frenzy as we bring 2020 to a close.<br /><br />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Workshops\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'scott-kildall', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 'event', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection', 'art-tech-festival-2020-joynt'),
(163, 'SnipSynth Talk', 'snipsynth-talk', '2020-12-18', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/snipsynth-talk-and-meet-the-artist.png', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Part of the 10th annual <a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a> (included in the</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a>&nbsp;)</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Friday, Dec 18th, 2020, 6:00pm&nbsp;PST&nbsp; (check your&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">\"SnipSynth\" is a new 6-channel granular synthesizer that Scott Kildall has developed based on his work on installations such as Botanic Quartet. He will discuss it and the underlying architecture, which is an ESP32 chip with custom synth classes that he\'s written. The control bay will be 3d-printed and includes controls for loading small snips of WAV files, varying grain size/offset along with control voltages. This wil be available as open source and should be less than $100 in parts. Tune in!&nbsp;<br /><br />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival Tickets\" /></a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>', 'scott-kildall', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 'event', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection', 'art-tech-festival-2020-joynt'),
(183, 'Create LED Patterns for Entwined', 'create-led-patterns-for-entwined', '2021-02-13', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/create-led-patterns-for-entwined.png', '<center>Saturday, February 13th @ <a href=\"https://time.is/11:00AM_13_February_2021_in_San_Francisco/New_York/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\" target=\"_blank\">11:00AM (PST)</a></center><center></center><center></center><center></center><center></center>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://buytickets.at/codame/483145/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<h3><strong><span style=\"font-family: Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span></strong>Build LED patterns using Processing and watch them come to life in Golden Gate Park\'s Peacock Meadow! Entwined is an installation by <a href=\"https://www.charlesgadeken.com/\">Charles Gadeken</a> composed of 2000 LED lights decorating large metal trees and shrubs. Learn how to build patterns for this installation so that your signature style can be on display for all of San Francisco to enjoy!<br /><br />In this workshop we will teach you the foundations you\'ll need to be able to write LX Studio patterns for Entwined Meadows.<br /><br />Some familiarity with Java or any object oriented programming required, as we\'ll be using Processing. You\'ll need is a computer with a stable internet connection, Chrome, and a Google login account.&nbsp;Get a head start by having some fun ideas of what you think would make some great patterns!<br />&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://buytickets.at/codame/483145/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž&nbsp;SCHEDULE ã€&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Sat, Feb 13th, 2020</li>\r\n<li class=\"graf graf--li\">11&nbsp;amâ€Š&mdash;â€Š 1 pm PT (2 hours)&nbsp;<a class=\"markup--anchor markup--li-anchor\" href=\"https://time.is/11:00AM_13_February_2021_in_San_Francisco/New_York/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-href=\"https://time.is/1100AM_18_October_2020_in_San_Francisco/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\">Check your timezone</a>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž SKILL LEVEL ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Some basic understanding of Java or object-oriented programming required.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž WORKSHOP OUTLINE ã€</h3>\r\n<ol start=\"1\" type=\"1\">\r\n<li>Troubleshooting -- Making sure we\'re all starting on the same foot!</li>\r\n<li>Introductions (The Artist, The Sculpture)</li>\r\n<li>The Basics (UI Walkthrough, Creating simple patterns)</li>\r\n<li><em>Breakout: Exploring simple patterns</em></li>\r\n<li>The Advanced (More Advanced pattern techniques)<em><br /></em></li>\r\n<li><em>Breakout: Playing with what you know</em></li>\r\n<li>Show and Tell</li>\r\n<li>Instructor Q&amp;A</li>\r\n<li>How to get your pattern onto Entwined</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž ATTENDEES BRING ã€</h3>\r\n<p>1. Have <strong>Processing 3</strong> installed and ready to go (documentation provided below)</p>\r\n<p>2. Have <strong>Entwined</strong> repo downloaded and ready (documentation provided below)</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Computer &amp; power/charger.</li>\r\n<li>Zoom installed ahead of time.</li>\r\n<li>Optional: 2nd monitor or screen so you can see the Zoom while working.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž CODAME PROVIDES ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Instructor Slides</li>\r\n<li>Documentation on getting setup,&nbsp;plus helpful information/instructions (<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Q-tmy1sxg6ZH_3IyOlrIx1kU09Mq2iiKhImZOlfE09Y/edit?usp=sharing\">click here!</a>)&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://buytickets.at/codame/483145/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/fY6FC0_RHxc\" width=\"425\" height=\"350\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/uploaded_images/entwined01.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/uploaded_images/entwined02.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"/uploaded_images/entwined03.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/uploaded_images/entwined05.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><em>(Photos by Joey Yee)</em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://buytickets.at/codame/483145/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž CODAME&nbsp;#CodeArtTogether Workshops ã€</h3>\r\n<table style=\"height: 101px;\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸ§ âœ¨</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Connect</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-81f37ba5-7fff-97be-c713-6edc787897a0\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸš§ðŸŽ¨</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Create</span></span></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸ¤©ðŸ’¬ </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Celebrate</span></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Connecting, Creating, and Celebrating&nbsp;are pillars of the&nbsp;<a href=\"/projects/code-art-together\">CODAME #CodeArtTogether workshops</a>!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Workshops are great for team building, remote or IRL. They cultivate space to play, which guides sense-making and sparks innovation. Attendees become featured artists with the option to show their workshop creations in CODAME galleries.&nbsp;<a href=\"/projects/code-art-together\">Learn more about this exciting offering</a><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/checkout/view-event/id/486392/chk/4cfa/?modal_widget=true&amp;widget=true&amp;d\">!</a></p>\r\n<p>What topics grab your curiosity to learn or teach?&nbsp;Let us know through our&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/call-for-workshops\">call for workshops</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/join-us\">Join us</a>&nbsp;as a sponsor, volunteer, or workshop leader!&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center>ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</center>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">CODAME is a member of Intersection for the Arts&nbsp;<br />a non profit 501(c)(3)&nbsp;organization.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">All proceeds will be split with the participating artists.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.flipcause.com/secure/cause_pdetails/NjU0OA==\">Donations</a>&nbsp;are always welcome.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thank you for your support for ART &hearts;ï¸ TECH !!!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/pages/code-of-conduct\">Code of Conduct</a>&nbsp;for all attendees.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>', 'colin-hunt,charles-gadeken', '', '', '', '', '', '0', 'workshop', '', ''),
(166, 'Recipes Embedded, Developed, and Created with Algorithms', 'recipes-embedded-developed-and-created-with-algorithms', '2020-12-19', 'https://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/recipes-embedded-developed-and-created-with-algorithms.png', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Part of the 10th annual <a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a> (included in the</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a>&nbsp;)</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Saturday, Dec 19, 2020, 10:00 AM PST (1 hour) (check your&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Please add to the <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1Q8a3ddfPA_-Zc8Gzvd0jlhdLO3N1LCI4DUYTNdHkRbk/edit#gid=777483841\">c0d3 kitchen GUESTBOOK</a>, by sharing your thoughts before&nbsp;the event -&nbsp;drop a comment, add a note or share an image.&nbsp;<br /><br />Transcend Taste is a digital exploration of how dining is an immersive experience. When people think of dining and food, their cultural and personal preferences are shown. From being a picky eater to collaborations for the betterment of the taste buds. One thing we forget at times is how this entity of object has the ability to make us wonder through both positive and negative connotations, depending on what is being discussed. In our performance/immersive installation, we will be breaking down the dining experience through different lenses. Particularly aiming at the 5 senses while reevaluating the meaning of some of our semantics towards this experience.<br /><br />Through different creative coding environments in conjunction with online spaces meant for exploration, c0d3 kitchen will be showcasing the kitchen in a deconstructed format. Where obejcts and sense will be and will not be how they normally are to promote thinking. A timeless performance that depending on your mood and how you interact with the space will bring upon a different sensation every time. Should be noted, it won\'t necessarily be a drastic change but one that emulates the ability to feel different, even if eating the same food twice.<br /><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>', 'illest-preacha,elena-kauffmann,kevin-smuggles', 'art-tech-festival-2020-joynt,transcending-taste-in-c0d3-kitchen', '', 'd2d-art', '', '', '0', 'event', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection', 'art-tech-festival-2020-joynt'),
(167, 'Anytime Experiences @ ART+TECH Festival 2020 /// JOYNT', 'anytime-experiences-art-tech-festival-2020-joynt', '2020-12-11', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/anytime-experiences-art-tech-festival-2020-joynt.png', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a>&nbsp;to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT&nbsp;</strong></em><em>for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>The 10th annual ART+TECH Festival&nbsp;&nbsp;includes the following Anytime Experiences:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><a href=\"/projects/nexus\">Nexus: Collective Reflections Ornament Creation</a>&nbsp;by Quinn Keck</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://codame.com/projects/cangjie-s-poetry\">Cangjie\'s Poetry</a>&nbsp;by Weidl Zhang &amp; Donghao Ren</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://codame.com/projects/m-carbon-dioxide\">M Carbon Dioxide</a>&nbsp;by Sven Eberwein</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/projects/cosmos\">Cosmos&nbsp;</a>by Ivan Moreno</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/projects/vr-music-videos\">VR Music Videos: Conrad Greenleaf, Richard In Your Mind, Vape Dadz</a>&nbsp;by The Bad Lament</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/events/regalia-chromology-and-pilgrimage\">Projects by Fabin Rasheed: Regalia, Chromology, and Pilgrimage</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/projects/minecraft-art-tech-gallery\">CODAME\'s ART + TECH&nbsp;Minecraft Gallery</a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/projects/i-don-t-know-look-at-it\">\"I DON\'T KNOW. LOOK AT IT.\" Gallery Show</a>&nbsp;by Erica Anderson</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/projects/secrets-exchange-crypto-art-generator\">Secrets Exchange/Crypto Art Generator</a>&nbsp;by Lynette Lee</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/projects/harddiskmuseum\">Harddiskmuseum</a> by Solim&aacute;n L&oacute;pez&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/projects/paras-digital-art-cards\">Paras Digital Art Cards</a> - by Vicente Montelongo</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/projects/glitch-me\">Glitch-Me</a>&nbsp;by Naoto Hieda and Flor de Fuego</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/projects/transcending-taste-in-c0d3-kitchen\">Transcending Taste In c0d3 Kitchen</a> by&nbsp;Illest Preacha, Kevin Smuggles and Elena Kauffmann</li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/projects/spaces-gallery\">Spaces Gallery</a> by Ben Ha and Alex Shortt</li>\r\n</ul>', 'soliman-lopez,illest-preacha,elena-kauffmann,kevin-smuggles,ivan-moreno,quinn-keck,hufo,lynette-lee,erica-anderson,michelle-brown,soli,weidi-zhang,donghao-ren', 'harddiskmuseum,transcending-taste-in-c0d3-kitchen,cosmos,nexus,minecraft-art-tech-gallery,secrets-exchange-crypto-art-generator,i-don-t-know-look-at-it,vr-music-videos,cangjie-s-poetry', '', '', '', '', '0', 'event', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection', 'art-tech-festival-2020-joynt'),
(168, 'Live Events @ ART+TECH Festival 2020 /// JOYNT', 'live-events-art-tech-festival-2020-joynt', '2020-12-11', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/live-events-art-tech-festival-2020-joynt.png', '<p>The 10th annual ART+TECH Festival&nbsp;&nbsp;includes the following&nbsp;Live&nbsp;Events</p>\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a>&nbsp;to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT&nbsp;</strong></em><em>for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'elena-kauffmann,kevin-smuggles,eliza-struthers-jobin,scott-kildall,michael-noonan,illest-preacha,qiuwen-li,bruno-ruviaro,aastha-chawla,josh-mitchell,michelle-brown,soliman-lopez,sam-wray,tim-pietrusky,ilithya,quinn-keck,fabin-rasheed', 'nexus,harddiskmuseum,regalia,chromology,pilgrimage', '', '', '', '', '0', 'event', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection', 'recipes-embedded-developed-and-created-with-algorithms, sclork-20x20, snipsynth-talk, creating-vr-music-videos, botanic-quartet, harddiskmuseum-tour, modv-audio-visual-live-performance, curiously-minded-live-coding-shaders, collective-reflections, egalia-chromology-and-pilgrimage'),
(169, 'Glitch-me Introduction', 'glitch-me-introduction', '2020-12-18', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/glitch-me-introduction.png', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Part of the 10th annual <a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a> (included in the</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a>&nbsp;)</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Friday, Dec 18, 2020, 10:30 AM PST (30 min) (check your&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The project is a work-in-progress online platform for networked performances, which aims to introduce performative coding experiences to non-coders. When opened on a browser, the website shows a fullscreen-canvas of analog-synthesizer-inspired glitches, which may operate on a webcam feed, using Hydra live-coding environment created by a collaborator, Olivia Jack. In addition to showing &ldquo;video effects,&rdquo; multiple buttons and sliders appear on the webpage that trigger different video sources including webcam and effects; moreover, the trigger is also sent to other browsers opened online, in other words, everyone can influence each other&rsquo;s video feed with or without the knowledge of programming language. This opens up opportunities to online art-technology collaboration in different ways, for example, to be used for a networked performance between a dancer and a digital artist or a casual video call in which participants trigger different effects to add intimacy to the communication.</p>\r\n<p>Although the project is under development, we would like to use the opportunity either as a workshop/coding-jam format to discuss ideas with people interested in networked performance; or as a lecture-performance to present a new dimension of online collaboration using glitches, body and code. In both scenarios, we continue developing the platform (html, css, javascript) during the presentation in a performative manner and it stays as an online installation to be accessed any time.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>', 'naoto-hieda,flor-de-fuego', 'glitch-me', '', 'd2d-art', '', '', '0', 'event', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection', 'art-tech-festival-2020-joynt'),
(170, 'Build VR with JS', 'build-vr-with-js', '2020-12-12', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/build-vr-with-js.png', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Part of the 10th annual <a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Saturday, Dec 12, 2020, 3:00 PM (2.5 hour) (check your&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Join the Spaces team to build your very own WebVR experience. The SpacesVR development framework makes it easy to develop and create immersive experiences in the web. Prior knowledge of React is advised but not mandatory. At the end of the workshop, you will know the basics of React and React Three Fiber, familiar with the Spaces VR framework, as well as having your own custom Web VR experience for you take home.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/463044#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a>&nbsp;to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT&nbsp;</strong></em><em>for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž SKILL LEVEL ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Required: Programing fundamentals and some experience programming JavaScript.&nbsp; </span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Recommended: React.js and Three.js experience.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž WORKSHOP OUTLINE ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Participants will be given some assets to begin building a 3D world and after showing the basics on how to maneuver the code they will get the chance to implement some of their own functionality.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž ATTENDES BRING ã€</h3>\r\n<p>Environment setup:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Get a free <a href=\"https://codesandbox.io/\">Codesandbox</a> account.</li>\r\n<li>Clone this <a href=\"https://codesandbox.io/s/polished-meadow-erzku?fontsize=14&amp;hidenavigation=1&amp;theme=dark\" target=\"_blank\">codesandbox project</a>&nbsp;before hand, that will be our starting point. It uses the <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/spacesvr\" target=\"_blank\">spacesvr</a>&nbsp;package.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>and the usual:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Computer &amp; power/charger.</li>\r\n<li>Zoom installed ahead of time.</li>\r\n<li>Optional: 2nd monitor or screen so you can see the Zoom while working.</li>\r\n<li>Hop on the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/pk3C8DB\">CODAME Discord</a>&nbsp;if you have questions!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž CODAME PROVIDES ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Slides TBA</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: 400;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž SCHEDULE ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Sat, Dec 19th, 2020</li>\r\n<li>3:00 PM to 5:30 PM&nbsp;PST&nbsp;<a href=\"https://time.is/11:30AM_19_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\">Check your timezone</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž CODAME&nbsp;#CodeArtTogether Workshops ã€</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 101px;\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸ§ âœ¨</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Connect</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-81f37ba5-7fff-97be-c713-6edc787897a0\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸš§ðŸŽ¨</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Create</span></span></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸ¤©ðŸ’¬ </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Celebrate</span></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Connecting, Creating, and Celebrating&nbsp;are pillars of the&nbsp;<a href=\"/projects/code-art-together\">CODAME #CodeArtTogether workshops</a>!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Workshops are great for team building, remote or IRL. They cultivate space to play, which guides sense-making and sparks innovation. Attendees become featured artists with the option to show their workshop creations in CODAME galleries.&nbsp;<a href=\"/projects/code-art-together\">Learn more about this exciting offering</a><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/checkout/view-event/id/486392/chk/4cfa/?modal_widget=true&amp;widget=true&amp;d\">!</a></p>\r\n<p>What topics grab your curiosity to learn or teach?&nbsp;Let us know through our&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/call-for-workshops\">call for workshops</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/join-us\">#JOYNT US</a>&nbsp;as a sponsor, volunteer, or workshop leader!</p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/463044#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a>&nbsp;to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT&nbsp;</strong></em><em>for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center>ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</center>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">CODAME is a member of Intersection for the Arts&nbsp;<br />a non profit 501(c)(3)&nbsp;organization.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">All proceeds will be split with the participating artists.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.flipcause.com/secure/cause_pdetails/NjU0OA==\">Donations</a>&nbsp;are always welcome.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thank you for your support for ART &hearts;ï¸ TECH !!!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/pages/code-of-conduct\">Code of Conduct</a>&nbsp;for all attendees.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!--\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://www.eventbrite.com/custombutton?eid=34741461647\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Workshops\" /></a></p>\r\n-->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n|-- End TT Button -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n|------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'ben-ha,alex-shortt', 'spaces-gallery,art-tech-festival-2020-joynt', '', '', '', '', '0', 'workshop', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/463044#ticket_selection', 'art-tech-festival-2020-joynt'),
(176, 'Behind the Screens With Sven Eberwein', 'behind-the-screens-with-sven-eberwein', '2020-12-15', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/behind-the-screens-with-sven-eberwein.png', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Part of the 10th annual <a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a> (included in the</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a>&nbsp;)</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tuesday, Dec 15, 2020, 12:00 PM PST (45 min) (check your&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>Hosted by MoCDA and KnownOrigin.<br /><br />Sven Eberwein will discuss his work&nbsp;C Carbon Dioxide I &amp; II / M Carbon Dioxide and mission in creating art to represent and raise environmental awareness.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>C Carbon Dioxide I &amp; II&nbsp;will&nbsp;each represent 100 tonnes of CO2 reduction will be minted on KnownOrigin. This work will be listed in the exact dollar amount required to offset the corresponding CO2 reduction and acts only as a transmitter.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/uploaded_images/Schedule_(Day_Version).jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/3E6aQpKwO_Y\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>', 'sven-eberwein', 'm-carbon-dioxide,art-tech-festival-2020-joynt', '', 'knownorigin,mocda', '', '', '0', 'event', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection', ''),
(172, 'CODAME at Github Universe 2020', 'codame-at-github-universe-2020', '2020-12-08', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/codame-at-github-universe-2020.png', '<p>As part of&nbsp; GitHub Universe &middot; Virtual 2020 &middot; Dec 8 - 10, 2020</p>\r\n<p>Get inspired with entertaining performances, tutorials, and unexpected stories, all driven by code. You\'ll hear from speakers exploring the intersection of technology and art, enjoy tutorials and performances by creative coders, and discover innovative projects that are challenging the boundaries of technology. Whether you\'re a seasoned software engineer or just starting out, now&rsquo;s your chance to play.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/BuiQbwcFsyA\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>The event&nbsp;is free and can be watch line on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://githubuniverse.com/play/\">https://githubuniverse.com/play/</a>&nbsp;</p>', 'eliza-struthers-jobin,ilithya,char-stiles,james-proctor,michelle,mobina-nouri,shaghayegh-cyrous,ash-herr,abhinay-khoparzi,samarth-gulati,crystal-glass,michelle-brown', '', 'github', '', '', '', '0', 'event', 'https://githubuniverse.com/play/', ''),
(173, 'Learn to DJ in VR with Tribe XR', 'learn-to-dj-in-vr-with-tribe-xr', '2020-12-15', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/learn-to-dj-in-vr-with-tribe-xr.png', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Part of the 10th annual&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Tuesday, Dec 15, 2020, 11:30 AM PST (1 hour) (check your&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Learn the fundamentals of DJing in this intro session with Ozan from the Tribe team. You&rsquo;ll review how to use the deck controls, touch on music theory, and learn how to do a high-energy mix.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/463340#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a>&nbsp;to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT&nbsp;</strong></em><em>for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž SKILL LEVEL ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Basic familiarity with VR space. </span>Requires an Oculus Rift or Quest headset</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž WORKSHOP OUTLINE ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">TBA</span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž ATTENDES BRING ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Requires an Oculus Rift or Quest headset.</li>\r\n<li>Attendes will need to provide their Oculus user names to connect to the Tribe XR space.</li>\r\n<li>Hop on the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/pk3C8DB\">CODAME Discord</a>&nbsp;if you have questions!</li>\r\n<li>Join <a href=\"https://discord.gg/tribexr\">TribeXR Discord</a> Channel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž CODAME PROVIDES ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Slides TBA</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž SCHEDULE ã€</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"text-align: center;\">Tue, Dec 15th</span>, 2020</li>\r\n<li><span style=\"text-align: center;\">11:30 AM to 12:30 AM</span>&nbsp;PST&nbsp;<a href=\"https://time.is/11:30AM_19_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\">Check your timezone</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>ã€Ž CODAME&nbsp;#CodeArtTogether Workshops ã€</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"height: 101px;\" width=\"100%\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸ§ âœ¨</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Connect</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\"><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-81f37ba5-7fff-97be-c713-6edc787897a0\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸš§ðŸŽ¨</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Create</span></span></td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.2; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">ðŸ¤©ðŸ’¬ </span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br /></span><span style=\"font-family: \'Source Serif Pro\', serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Celebrate</span></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Connecting, Creating, and Celebrating&nbsp;are pillars of the&nbsp;<a href=\"/projects/code-art-together\">CODAME #CodeArtTogether workshops</a>!&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Workshops are great for team building, remote or IRL. They cultivate space to play, which guides sense-making and sparks innovation. Attendees become featured artists with the option to show their workshop creations in CODAME galleries.&nbsp;<a href=\"/projects/code-art-together\">Learn more about this exciting offering</a><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/checkout/view-event/id/486392/chk/4cfa/?modal_widget=true&amp;widget=true&amp;d\">!</a></p>\r\n<p>What topics grab your curiosity to learn or teach?&nbsp;Let us know through our&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/call-for-workshops\">call for workshops</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/join-us\">#JOYNT US</a>&nbsp;as a sponsor, volunteer, or workshop leader!</p>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 100%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/463340#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a>&nbsp;to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT&nbsp;</strong></em><em>for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</em></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center>ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</center>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">CODAME is a member of Intersection for the Arts&nbsp;<br />a non profit 501(c)(3)&nbsp;organization.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">All proceeds will be split with the participating artists.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.flipcause.com/secure/cause_pdetails/NjU0OA==\">Donations</a>&nbsp;are always welcome.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thank you for your support for ART &hearts;ï¸ TECH !!!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/pages/code-of-conduct\">Code of Conduct</a>&nbsp;for all attendees.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'ozan-serim', 'art-tech-festival-2020-joynt', '', 'tribexr', '', '', '0', 'workshop', 'https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/463340#ticket_selection', 'art-tech-festival-2020-joynt');
