(60, 'Day 1: ART+TECH Festival 2020 ã€Ž JOYNT ã€', 'day-1-art-tech-festival-2020-joynt', '', '<div>\r\n<h2>Friday, Dec 11, 2020 Schedule</h2>\r\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">We are starting our first day of the Festival with a boom! 2 Live events and 1 workshop!</p>\r\n<table dir=\"ltr\" border=\"1\" width=\"650\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><colgroup><col width=\"63\" /><col width=\"80\" /><col width=\"276\" /></colgroup>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td data-sheets-value=\"{\" data-sheets-numberformat=\"{\">10:00 AM</td>\r\n<td data-sheets-value=\"{\">Live Event</td>\r\n<td data-sheets-value=\"{\" data-sheets-hyperlink=\"https://codame.com/events/how-to-integrate-art-science-technology-ai-into-public-spaces\"><a href=\"/events/how-to-integrate-art-science-technology-ai-into-public-spaces\" target=\"_blank\">New Age Of Renaissance: How to Integrate Art, Science, Technology &amp; AI into Public Spaces</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td data-sheets-value=\"{\" data-sheets-numberformat=\"{\">11:30 AM</td>\r\n<td data-sheets-value=\"{\">Workshop</td>\r\n<td data-sheets-value=\"{\" data-sheets-hyperlink=\"https://codame.com/events/mint-crypto-art-tokens\"><a href=\"/events/mint-crypto-art-tokens\" target=\"_blank\">Minting Crypto Art NFTs</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td data-sheets-value=\"{\" data-sheets-numberformat=\"{\">5:00 PM</td>\r\n<td data-sheets-value=\"{\">Live Event</td>\r\n<td data-sheets-value=\"{\" data-sheets-hyperlink=\"https://codame.com/events/happy-hour-on-discord\"><a href=\"/events/happy-hour-on-discord\" target=\"_blank\">Happy Hour</a></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">For existingã€Ž Live Events&nbsp;ã€+&nbsp;ã€ŽAll Pass ã€Ticket Holders:</h2>\r\n<p>Check your email with your password protected <a href=\"http://live.codame.com\">access list</a> of events.</p>\r\n<p>For any question&nbsp;or support, connect with us and the community on <a href=\"https://discord.gg/pk3C8DB\" target=\"_blank\">Discord</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a style=\"text-align: center;\" href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2>HOW TO INTEGRATE ART, SCIENCE, TECHNOLOGY &amp; AI INTO PUBLIC SPACES</h2>\r\n<p>10:00 AM PST (1 hour) (check your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/how-to-integrate-art-science-technology-ai-into-public-spaces.png\" alt=\"How to Integrate Art, Science, Technology &amp; AI into Public Spaces\" /></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Part of the 10th annual&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a>&nbsp;(included in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a>&nbsp;)</p>\r\n<p>Ouchhhh will present their artistic vision, innovative techniques and some of their latest creations with AI followed by a Q&amp;A session.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>From the very first moments of Ouchhh&rsquo;s journey as a studio, the relationship between the individual and the environment has been a main focus on how technology can inform and bridge our understanding of the physical and virtual worlds. The studio will touch on their journey and its experiential practices in different mediums by using art, science, technology and artificial intelligence.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>MINT CRYPTO ART TOKENS</h2>\r\n<p>11:30AM PST (<a href=\"https://time.is/11:30AM_11_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\" target=\"_blank\">timezone converter</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/mint-crypto-art-tokens.png\" alt=\"Mint Crypto Art Tokens\" />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><center>\r\n<p id=\"&rdquo;fest-10&rdquo;\">Part of the&nbsp;10th&nbsp;annual&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></p>\r\n&nbsp;Make your mark on the Ethereum blockchain by minting your art as a crypto collectable! Before getting there we\'ll cover the fundementals of crypto art with Q&amp;A time to take the edge off the overwhelming terminology and concepts. The crypto art scene is an vibrant source of inspiration. Join the super connector ride where new light is being shed on the value of creativity... whether you\'re a traditional artist, animator, photographer, or other!&nbsp;</center><center></center><center></center>\r\n<table cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/463070#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a>&nbsp;to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT&nbsp;for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>HAPPY HOUR ON DISCORD</h2>\r\n<p>5 PM PST (<a href=\"https://time.is/500PM_11_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\" target=\"_blank\">check your timezone</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/happy-hour-on-discord.png\" alt=\"Happy Hour on Discord\" /></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Part of the 10th annual&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a>&nbsp;(included in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a>&nbsp;)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Join #happy-hour under General Voice on the CODAME Discord.</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Voice only so save our video-call-scorched retinas and let our hairs down.</li>\r\n<li>Bring WIP, inspirations, soap box, projects, remix chops, or nothing but your love of ART+TECH ðŸ‘¾</li>\r\n<li>Meet the team who put together CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020ã€Ž JOYNT ã€</li>\r\n<li>No format or agenda, just check out and chillax âœŒ</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"/uploaded_images/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt.gif\" alt=\"ART+TECH FESTIVAL 2020ã€Ž JOYNT ã€\" /></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">JOYNT&nbsp;=&nbsp;Connect&nbsp;+&nbsp;Create&nbsp;+&nbsp;Celebrate</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Let\'s&nbsp;JOYNT&nbsp;forces to nurture Diversity, Equity, &amp; Inclusion within the art and tech community!</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Artists are innovators and producers of creative and extraordinary ideas and visions. Experiencing art and artistic processes is an important opportunity for learning and exploration. Even more so, collaborative art is a transformational force to strengthen the community and enhance well-being. CODAME invites you to become an active participant at our Festival where you can connect, create, and celebrate with our Artists.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">CODAME is a member of Intersection for the Arts a non profit 501(c)(3) organization. All proceeds will be split with the participating artists.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thank you for your support for ART&nbsp;ðŸ’œ&nbsp;TECH !!!&nbsp;<a href=\"http://codame.com/pages/code-of-conduct\">Code of Conduct</a>&nbsp;for all attendees.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', '0'),
(61, 'DAY 2: ART+TECH FESTIVAL 2020 ã€Ž JOYNT ã€', 'day-2-art-tech-festival-2020-joynt', '', '<h2>Saturday, Dec 12, 2020 Schedule</h2>\r\n<p>Yesterday&nbsp;we kicked off the ART+TECH Festival <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/JOYNT?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#JOYNT</a>&nbsp;with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/starpause?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@starpause</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BrunoFonzi?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@BrunoFonzi</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/brandsinvr?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@brandsinvr</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/quinn_keck?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@quinn_keck</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/nataliiafrank?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@nataliiafrank</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lunaceee?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@lunaceee</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lizreidtw?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@lizreidtw</a>&nbsp;and Liz Reid</p>\r\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">It&rsquo;s time to CONNECT, CREATE, and CELEBRATE again! In the day 2 of the Festival we have one live event and two workshops!</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">10:00am (PST) - Live Event -&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/curiously-minded-live-coding-shaders\" target=\"_blank\">Curiously Minded: Live Coding Shaders</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">11:30am (PST) - Workshop -&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/compose-music-with-code\" target=\"_blank\">Compose Generative Music With Gibber</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">03:00am&nbsp;(PST) - Workshop -&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/build-a-vr-space-with-spaces\" target=\"_blank\">Build VR with JS</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/4qRPEwHY7eo?controls=0\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>\r\n<script src=\"//www.instagram.com/embed.js\" async=\"\"></script>\r\n</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">For existingã€Ž Live Events&nbsp;ã€+&nbsp;ã€ŽAll Pass ã€Ticket Holders:</h2>\r\n<p>Check your email with your password protected&nbsp;<a href=\"http://live.codame.com/\">access list</a>&nbsp;of events.</p>\r\n<p>For any question&nbsp;or support, connect with us and the community on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/pk3C8DB\" target=\"_blank\">Discord</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>CURIOUSLY MINDED: LIVE CODING SHADERS</h2>\r\n<p>Saturday, Dec 12, 2020, 10:00am PST (2 hours) (check your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><a href=\"/events/curiously-minded-live-coding-shaders\"><img src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/curiously-minded-live-coding-shaders.png\" alt=\"Curiously Minded: Live Coding Shaders\" /></a></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Part of the 10th annual&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Included in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">ilithya and Eliza combine creative forces to create colorful shaders. They will be live-coding in the same editor, visuals refreshing in real time and chatting with the audience throughout. This livestream performance will be the premier launch of their new Twitch Channel.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Workshops\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;The shader they code will be 2D, colorful, and inspired by optical illusion. They hope to showcase how much fun and approachable shaders can be - how infusing a few simple concepts into a couple of lines of code can yield some pretty intriguing and complex looking results that might even feel 3D!</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Shaders are an amazing tool for creativity, but can seem intimidating and might feel like a very advanced topic, especially when you\'re just starting out, or like them, are self-taught programmers with no academic background in Math or CS. In sharing their coding sessions, they hope to encourage and inspire others curious about shaders, to take a dive down the rabbit hole. Or just watch them having fun while they do!<br /><br />All donations made during this performance will go to:&nbsp;CODE2040&nbsp;-&nbsp;a nonprofit activating, connecting, and mobilizing the largest racial equity community in tech to dismantle the structural barriers that prevent the full participation and leadership of Black and Latinx technologists in the innovation economy.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>ilithya\'s work is also featured in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://shop.codame.com/collections/ilithya\">CODAME Shop</a>&nbsp;and can be viewed in the CODAME&nbsp;<a href=\"https://newart.city/show/codame\">New Art City Gallery</a>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>COMPOSE MUSIC WITH CODE</h2>\r\n<p>Saturday, December 12th @ 11:30AM PST (<a href=\"https://time.is/11:30AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\" target=\"_blank\">timezone converter</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/events/compose-music-with-code\"><img src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/compose-music-with-code.png\" alt=\"Compose Music With Code\" /></a>Part of the&nbsp;10th&nbsp;annual&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Wonder why they say Music is Math? Let us show you how to join the worlds of open source code, math, and electronic music production. Continuing our music making adventures from the Beats for Beginners workshop, we will use a subset of the Javascript programming language to create live music in the browser.&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;<a style=\"text-align: center;\" href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/460617#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">Or get the&nbsp;</span><a style=\"text-align: center;\" href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a><span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT&nbsp;for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>BUILD VR WITH JS</h2>\r\n<p>Saturday, Dec 12, 2020, 3:00 PM (2.5 hour) (check your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/events/build-a-vr-space-with-spaces\"><img src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/build-vr-with-js.png\" alt=\"Build VR with JS\" /></a>Part of the 10th annual&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Join the Spaces team to build your very own WebVR experience. The SpacesVR development framework makes it easy to develop and create immersive experiences in the web. Prior knowledge of React is advised but not mandatory. At the end of the workshop, you will know the basics of React and React Three Fiber, familiar with the Spaces VR framework, as well as having your own custom Web VR experience for you take home</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a>&nbsp;to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT&nbsp;for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt.gif\" alt=\"ART+TECH FESTIVAL 2020ã€Ž JOYNT ã€\" /></a></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">JOYNT&nbsp;=&nbsp;Connect&nbsp;+&nbsp;Create&nbsp;+&nbsp;Celebrate</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Let\'s&nbsp;JOYNT&nbsp;forces to nurture Diversity, Equity, &amp; Inclusion within the art and tech community!</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Artists are innovators and producers of creative and extraordinary ideas and visions. Experiencing art and artistic processes is an important opportunity for learning and exploration. Even more so, collaborative art is a transformational force to strengthen the community and enhance well-being. CODAME invites you to become an active participant at our Festival where you can connect, create, and celebrate with our Artists.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">CODAME is a member of Intersection for the Arts a non profit 501(c)(3) organization. All proceeds will be split with the participating artists.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thank you for your support for ART&nbsp;ðŸ’œ&nbsp;TECH !!!&nbsp;<a href=\"http://codame.com/pages/code-of-conduct\">Code of Conduct</a>&nbsp;for all attendees.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>', '', '0'),
(62, 'DAY 3: ART+TECH FESTIVAL 2020 ã€Ž JOYNT ã€', 'day-3-art-tech-festival-2020-joynt', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/day-3-art-tech-festival-2020-joynt.png', '<h2>Sunday, Dec 13, 2020 Schedule</h2>\r\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">Join the&nbsp;ART+TECH Festival Day&nbsp;3 with a workshop and two live events!</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">11:30am (PST) - Workshop -&nbsp;<a class=\"in-cell-link\" href=\"/events/build-your-being-in-spark-ar\" target=\"_blank\">Build Your Being in Spark AR</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">11:30am (PST) - Live Event -&nbsp;<a class=\"in-cell-link\" href=\"http://codame.com/events/modv-audio-visual-live-performance\" target=\"_blank\">modV Audio Visual Live Performance</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">03:00pm (PST) - Live Event&nbsp;-&nbsp;<a class=\"in-cell-link\" href=\"/events/festival-grounds-opening\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Grounds Opening</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For existingã€Ž Live Events&nbsp;ã€+&nbsp;ã€ŽAll Pass ã€Ticket Holders:</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Check your email with your password protected&nbsp;<a href=\"http://live.codame.com/\">access list</a>&nbsp;of events.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For any question&nbsp;or support, connect with us and the community on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/pk3C8DB\" target=\"_blank\">Discord</a>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>BUILD YOUR BEING IN SPARK AR</h2>\r\n<p>Sunday, December 13th @ 11:30AM PST (check your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://time.is/11:30AM_13_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\" target=\"_blank\">timezone</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<a href=\"/events/build-your-being-in-spark-ar\"><img src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/build-your-being-in-spark-ar.png\" alt=\"Build Your Being in Spark AR\" /></a>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><center>\r\n<p id=\"&rdquo;fest-10&rdquo;\">Part of the&nbsp;10th&nbsp;annual&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></p>\r\n</center>Bring your best face forward in augmented reality! In this beginners course, we&rsquo;re building our best selves in Spark AR, an augmented reality tool by Facebook. No coding is necessary - we&rsquo;ll be using features within Spark AR like the facetracker, facemesh, 3D models, animation, and patches. Come with your creative spirit, you will emerge from this course in your final form.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />&nbsp;<img src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a>&nbsp;to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT&nbsp;for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 11px;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<h2>MODV AUDIO VISUAL LIVE PERFORMANCE</h2>\r\n<p>Sunday, Dec 13, 2020, 11:30am PST (check your&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2><a href=\"http://codame.com/events/modv-audio-visual-live-performance\"><img src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/modv-audio-visual-live-performance.png\" alt=\"modV Audio Visual Live Performance \" /></a></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: center;\">Part of the 10th annual&nbsp;</span><a style=\"text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"http://codame.com/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">included in the&nbsp;</span><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\">Sam (aka 2xAA) and Tim (aka NERDDISCO) are working on the open source visuals software called modV to use the power of the web to bring fine visuals to everyone. When they are doing a live performance, 2xAA is doing music using his Game Boys and NERDDISCO is using some shaders from Shadertoy in modV to generate visuals based on the music from 2xAA. They want to show that everyone can use modV for their shows.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Workshops\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>FESTIVAL GROUNDS OPENING</h2>\r\n<p>Sunday 12/13 (2020) 3:00 PM PST (check your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://time.is/300PM_13_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\" target=\"_blank\">timezone</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><a href=\"/events/festival-grounds-opening\"><img src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/festival-grounds-opening.png\" alt=\"Festival Grounds Opening\" /></a></p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Part of the 10th annual&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">included in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Experience the art of CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020ã€Ž JOYNT ã€in a playful, game-like, multiplayer environment. Built in New Art City, a virtual exhibition space with a focus on copresence and native web technology.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Join the Zoom to where d0n.xyz and Yiyue Chen will share their inspirations and learnings from building New Art City and the Festival Grounds architecture. Lisa Kolb will share her initial vision to create a Festival Ground environment to house the Art+Tech experiences she curated for the Festival.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"text-align: center;\" href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Workshops\" /></a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt.gif\" alt=\"ART+TECH FESTIVAL 2020ã€Ž JOYNT ã€\" /></a></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">JOYNT&nbsp;=&nbsp;Connect&nbsp;+&nbsp;Create&nbsp;+&nbsp;Celebrate</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Let\'s&nbsp;JOYNT&nbsp;forces to nurture Diversity, Equity, &amp; Inclusion within the art and tech community!</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Artists are innovators and producers of creative and extraordinary ideas and visions. Experiencing art and artistic processes is an important opportunity for learning and exploration. Even more so, collaborative art is a transformational force to strengthen the community and enhance well-being. CODAME invites you to become an active participant at our Festival where you can connect, create, and celebrate with our Artists.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">CODAME is a member of Intersection for the Arts a non profit 501(c)(3) organization. All proceeds will be split with the participating artists.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Thank you for your support for ART&nbsp;ðŸ’œ&nbsp;TECH !!!&nbsp;<a href=\"http://codame.com/pages/code-of-conduct\">Code of Conduct</a>&nbsp;for all attendees.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `pages` (`id`, `name`, `slug`, `pic`, `description`, `old_url`, `hidden`) VALUES
(63, 'DAY 4: ART+TECH Festival 2020 ã€Ž JOYNT ã€', 'day-4-art-tech-festival-2020-joynt', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/day-4-art-tech-festival-2020-joynt.png', '<h2 style=\"text-align: left;\">Monday, Dec 14, 2020 Schedule</h2>\r\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\" style=\"text-align: left;\">ã€Ž JOYNT ã€ the&nbsp;ART+TECH Festival Day&nbsp;4 by attending today\'s events:</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\" style=\"text-align: left;\">10:00am (PST) - Live Event&nbsp;-&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/harddiskmuseum-tour\" target=\"_blank\">Harddiskmuseum Tour</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\" style=\"text-align: left;\">11:30am (PST) -&nbsp;Workshop&nbsp;-&nbsp;<a href=\"http://codame.com/events/e-lit-games-playing-with-words\" target=\"_blank\">E-Lit Games (Playing With Words)</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For existingã€Ž Live Events&nbsp;ã€+&nbsp;ã€ŽAll Pass ã€Ticket Holders:</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Check your email with&nbsp;the password protected&nbsp;<a href=\"http://live.codame.com/\">access list</a>&nbsp;of events.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">For any question&nbsp;or support, connect with us and the community on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/pk3C8DB\" target=\"_blank\">Discord</a>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2>HARDDISKMUSEUM TOUR</h2>\r\n<p>Monday, Dec 14, 2020, 10:00am PST (check your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 650px;\" src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/harddiskmuseum-tour.png\" alt=\"Harddiskmuseum Tour\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Part of the 10th annual&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a>&nbsp;(included in the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a>&nbsp;)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The Harddiskmuseum is a Museum of digital and new media art content based in a hard drive of 2TB founded by the artist Solim&aacute;n L&oacute;pez in 2015.&nbsp;Now in 2020 the Museum includes the pieces of 110 artists from more than 20 different countries. Artworks of video, static images, video games, text, audio pieces, interactive pieces and a long etc.. are part of this unique repository.&nbsp; At the end of 2020 the Museum will have its version in genetic code. The first Museum in history to store its content in DNA.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Workshops\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>E-LIT GAMES (PLAYING WITH WORDS)</h2>\r\n<p>Monday, December 14th @ 11:30AM PST (<a href=\"https://time.is/11:30AM_14_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\" target=\"_blank\">timezone converter</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/e-lit-games-playing-with-words.png\" alt=\"E-lit Games (Playing With Words)\" /></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><center>Part of the&nbsp;10th&nbsp;annual&nbsp;<a href=\"http://codame.com/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></center></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Interested in generative poetry and electronic literature? Through collaborative coding projects, we will learn how to build games based on the written word, in the browser. These interactive games will have something in common: they all try to help with the writer\'s block! Bring your imaginary worlds and your creativity to this workshop as we will code interactive games where writing is the main action.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><center></center><center><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/460516#ticket_selection\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></center>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Or get the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a>&nbsp;to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT&nbsp;for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt.gif\" alt=\"ART+TECH FESTIVAL 2020ã€Ž JOYNT ã€\" /></a></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">JOYNT&nbsp;=&nbsp;Connect&nbsp;+&nbsp;Create&nbsp;+&nbsp;Celebrate</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Let\'s&nbsp;JOYNT&nbsp;forces to nurture Diversity, Equity, &amp; Inclusion within the art and tech community!</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Artists are innovators and producers of creative and extraordinary ideas and visions. Experiencing art and artistic processes is an important opportunity for learning and exploration. Even more so, collaborative art is a transformational force to strengthen the community and enhance well-being. CODAME invites you to become an active participant at our Festival where you can connect, create, and celebrate with our Artists.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">CODAME is a member of Intersection for the Arts a non profit 501(c)(3) organization. All proceeds will be split with the participating artists.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Thank you for your support for ART&nbsp;ðŸ’œ&nbsp;TECH !!!&nbsp;<a href=\"http://codame.com/pages/code-of-conduct\">Code of Conduct</a>&nbsp;for all attendees.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>', '', '0'),
(65, 'DAY 6: ART+TECH Festival 2020ã€Ž JOYNT ã€', 'day-6-art-tech-festival-2020-joynt', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/day-6-art-tech-festival-2020-joynt.png', '<h2>Wednesday, Dec 16, 2020 Schedule</h2>\r\n<p class=\"graf graf--p\">ã€Ž JOYNT ã€ the&nbsp;ART+TECH Festival Day 6. Connect, Create and Celebrate with us at:</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">10:00am (PST) - Live Event&nbsp;-&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/async-art-cryptovoxels-tour\" target=\"_blank\">Async Art Cryptovoxels Tour</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">11:30am (PST) -&nbsp;Workshop&nbsp;-&nbsp;<a href=\"http://codame.com/events/modular-audio-visualisation-with-modv\" target=\"_blank\">Modular Audio Visualisation with modV</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">05:30pm (PST) - Live Event&nbsp;-&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/ar-vr-art-and-storytelling\" target=\"_blank\">AR/VR Art and Storytelling</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">06:00pm (PST) - Workshop&nbsp;-&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/wild-goose-moving-meditation\" target=\"_blank\">Wild Goose Moving Meditation</a></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>For existingã€Ž Live Events&nbsp;ã€+&nbsp;ã€ŽAll Pass ã€Ticket Holders:</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" lang=\"en\">Check your email with&nbsp;the password protected&nbsp;<a href=\"http://live.codame.com/\">access list</a>&nbsp;of events.</p>\r\n<p>For any question&nbsp;or support, connect with us and the community on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/pk3C8DB\" target=\"_blank\">Discord</a>.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</p>\r\n<div class=\"bar-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #dfdfdf; float: left; width: 650px; background: #1d1a1c; border-width: 1px 0px; border-image: initial; padding-left: 10px; margin: 20px 0px; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; border-color: #333333 initial #333333 initial; border-style: solid initial solid initial;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; font-size: 30px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 10px 0px; margin: 0px;\">ASYNC ART CRYPTOVOXELS TOUR</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 650px; color: #ffffff; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: start; background-color: #000000;\" src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/async-art-cryptovoxels-tour.png\" alt=\"Async Art Cryptovoxels Tour\" /></p>\r\n<div class=\"text-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; padding: 20px 0px; color: #ffffff; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #000000;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Go on a tour of the Async Art Gallery in Cryptovoxels! We will also be livestreaming this event if you want to watch from Twitch.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Sam Brukhman&nbsp;from Async Art will be your tour guide.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">A virtual world powered by the Ethereum blockchain. Players can&nbsp;buy land&nbsp;and build stores and art galleries. Editing tools, avatars and text chat are built in. There are over 300 art galleries to explore in Cryptovoxels.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</p>\r\n<div class=\"bar-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #dfdfdf; float: left; width: 650px; background: #1d1a1c; border-width: 1px 0px; border-image: initial; padding-left: 10px; margin: 20px 0px; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; border-color: #333333 initial #333333 initial; border-style: solid initial solid initial;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; font-size: 30px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 10px 0px; margin: 0px;\">MODULAR AUDIO VISUALISATION WITH MODV</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 650px; color: #ffffff; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: start; background-color: #000000;\" src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/modular-audio-visualisation-with-modv.png\" alt=\"Modular Audio Visualisation with modV\" /></p>\r\n<div class=\"text-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; padding: 20px 0px; color: #ffffff; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #000000;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\">Wed, Dec 16 @ 11:30AM PT (<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://time.is/11:30AM_16_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\">time.is localizer</a>) for 2.5 hours.</p>\r\n<p id=\"&rdquo;fest-10&rdquo;\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Part of the&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">10th</strong>&nbsp;annual&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"http://codame.com/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\">By using the open source software modV you will be able to create audio reactive visualisations by combining different kinds of visual modules (2D, Interactive Shader Format and WebGL Shader) with any kind of audio input like a microphone or your favorite music. In the end you will know all the basics in order to do your first live performance as a VJ.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 650px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/460616#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Or get the&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\">ALL ACCESS pass</a>&nbsp;to CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020 #JOYNT&nbsp;</strong></em><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">for 10 days of Workshops, Live Events, and Anytime Experiences!</em>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</p>\r\n<div class=\"bar-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #dfdfdf; float: left; width: 650px; background: #1d1a1c; border-width: 1px 0px; border-image: initial; padding-left: 10px; margin: 20px 0px; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; border-color: #333333 initial #333333 initial; border-style: solid initial solid initial;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; font-size: 30px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 10px 0px; margin: 0px;\">AR/VR ART AND STORYTELLING</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 650px; color: #ffffff; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: start; background-color: #000000;\" src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/ar-vr-art-and-storytelling.png\" alt=\"AR/VR Art and Storytelling\" /></p>\r\n<div class=\"text-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; padding: 20px 0px; color: #ffffff; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #000000;\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\">Part of the 10th annual&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a>&nbsp;(included in the&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a>&nbsp;)</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\">Wednesday, Dec 16, 2020, 5:30 pm PST (check your&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://time.is/1000AM_12_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/London/Berlin/Hyderabad?CODAME\">timezone</a>)<span id=\"docs-internal-guid-a7336780-7fff-43db-e918-f1975363585d\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Watch artist Marc O Matic create live and talk about AR/VR Art and Storytelling. He will be available for questions throughout and will be minting the piece he creates on CryptoArt Platform SuperRare available for sale following the event.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Workshops\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ðŸ’Ÿ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’œ ðŸ‘¾ ðŸ’Ÿ</p>\r\n<div class=\"bar-link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #dfdfdf; float: left; width: 650px; background: #1d1a1c; border-width: 1px 0px; border-image: initial; padding-left: 10px; margin: 20px 0px; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; border-color: #333333 initial #333333 initial; border-style: solid initial solid initial;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; font-size: 30px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 10px 0px; margin: 0px;\">WILD GOOSE MOVING MEDITATION</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; width: 650px; color: #ffffff; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: start; background-color: #000000;\" src=\"http://codame.com/uploaded_images/wild-goose-moving-meditation.png\" alt=\"Wild Goose Moving Meditation\" /></p>\r\n<div class=\"text-content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 15px; padding: 20px 0px; color: #ffffff; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; background-color: #000000;\"><center style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Wed, Dec 16th @ 6:00PM&nbsp;PST (<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://time.is/6:00PM_16_December_2020_in_San_Francisco/New_York/Berlin/Hyderabad/Shanghai?CODAME\" target=\"_blank\">timezone converter</a>)</center>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<center style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<p id=\"&rdquo;fest-10&rdquo;\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Part of the&nbsp;<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">10th</strong>&nbsp;annual&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: left;\">Wild Goose Moving Meditation is a rough translation of Dayan Qigong (å¤§é›æ°—åŠŸ). This Qigong is focused on well being, balance, flexibility, mind-body connection, and play. The form is easy to learn and adaptable for students of all ages and fitness levels. There\'s no need for mats or special clothes, making it a perfect break around the office or anywhere you can pause for presence.</p>\r\n</center>\r\n<table style=\"background-color: #351e58; width: 650px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" cellpadding=\"10px\">\r\n<tbody style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<tr style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<td style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/463353#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #000000; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Festival 2020\" /></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: center;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Or get the&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #00a4a7 !important;\" href=\