(77, 'ART+TECH NEWS - June 8th, 2023', 'art-tech-news---june-8th-2023', '', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">RC Animatronics&nbsp;| Franck Vigroux NACHT&nbsp;| #minacoding all month&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ART+TECH inspiration curated by team CODAME&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"pullquote\" data-pm-slice=\"2 1 []\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://codame.substack.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Sign Up</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://codame.com/pages/support-art-tech\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Support</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1><code><strong>PROJECTS <br /><br /><img src=\"/uploaded_images/ezgif-2-9096ee5a2d.gif\" alt=\"\" /><br /></strong></code></h1>\r\n<p>Danny Huynh animatronics are as functional as they are beautiful. His creations are fully operational RC vehicles. His channel has&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@DannyHuynhCreations/featured\" target=\"_blank\">9 years of animatronic RC action and builds</a>!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\r\n<figure><source srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3ab2e89e-33f3-41c3-8a6b-456b8c9d2edb_600x338.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3ab2e89e-33f3-41c3-8a6b-456b8c9d2edb_600x338.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3ab2e89e-33f3-41c3-8a6b-456b8c9d2edb_600x338.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3ab2e89e-33f3-41c3-8a6b-456b8c9d2edb_600x338.gif 1456w\" type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"100vw\" />\r\n<div class=\"image2-inset\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1><code><strong>EVENTS </strong></code></h1>\r\n<div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\r\n<figure><source srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F45211919-1a52-44e2-ac09-3160f57da8fe_2480x1467.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F45211919-1a52-44e2-ac09-3160f57da8fe_2480x1467.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F45211919-1a52-44e2-ac09-3160f57da8fe_2480x1467.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F45211919-1a52-44e2-ac09-3160f57da8fe_2480x1467.jpeg 1456w\" type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"100vw\" />\r\n<div class=\"image2-inset\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><img src=\"/uploaded_images/ga_ezgif-2-9c4ab0c502.gif\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Franck Vigroux performs ATOTAL, fusing beats &amp; hypnotic projections, &amp; premieres NACHT, a phantasmagorical journey in sensory immersion on June 16th @ Gray Area.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://grayarea.org/event/recombinant-media-labs-presents-franck-vigroux/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Buy Tickets</a>!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h1 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><code><strong>OPPORTUNITIES</strong><code> <br /><br /></code></code></h1>\r\n<pre data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">&nbsp;</pre>\r\n<div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\r\n<figure><source srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb85e1304-82ac-4c07-b293-86d4cd726d2e_320x320.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb85e1304-82ac-4c07-b293-86d4cd726d2e_320x320.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb85e1304-82ac-4c07-b293-86d4cd726d2e_320x320.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb85e1304-82ac-4c07-b293-86d4cd726d2e_320x320.gif 1456w\" type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"100vw\" />\r\n<div class=\"image2-inset\"><img class=\"sizing-normal\" title=\"\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb85e1304-82ac-4c07-b293-86d4cd726d2e_320x320.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb85e1304-82ac-4c07-b293-86d4cd726d2e_320x320.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb85e1304-82ac-4c07-b293-86d4cd726d2e_320x320.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fb85e1304-82ac-4c07-b293-86d4cd726d2e_320x320.gif 1456w\" alt=\"\" width=\"\" height=\"\" data-attrs=\"{\" />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<figcaption class=\"image-caption\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/imSunny55/status/1666811024790659083\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">OYASUMI by @imSunny55</a></figcaption></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>If you liked&nbsp;<a class=\"css-4rbku5 css-18t94o4 css-901oao css-16my406 r-1cvl2hr r-1loqt21 r-poiln3 r-bcqeeo r-qvutc0\" href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/genuary?src=hashtag_click\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">#genuary</a>&nbsp;your should try&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/minacoding?src=hashtag_click\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">#minacoding</a>, a super wholesome creative coding challenge for the month of June. Check out the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ginzi_o/status/1661509012997935104\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">prompts for daily inspiration</a>!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1><code><strong>SPONSORS&nbsp;</strong></code></h1>\r\n<p>Be recognized as a visionary supporter of CODAME.&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/support-art-tech\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Sponsor the ART+TECH Newsletter</a>!</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Thanks for joining us! See you in a week &amp; don&rsquo;t forget to submit your exciting Interviews, Projects, Events, Workshops, and Call For Proposals to the CODAME ART+TECH Newsletter&hellip;&nbsp;<a href=\"/projects/art-tech-newsletter\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">right here</a>!</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Subscribe</h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe style=\"border-style: solid; border-color: #eeeeee; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-color: white;\" src=\"https://codame.substack.com/embed\" width=\"480\" height=\"320\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -28px; top: 1385.68px;\">&nbsp;</div>', '', '0'),
(78, 'ART+TECH News - June 22nd, 2023', 'art-tech-news---june-22nd-2023', '', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Fun Pants&nbsp;| Game Character Design Workshop&nbsp;| Open Calls</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ART+TECH inspiration curated by team CODAME&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"pullquote\" data-pm-slice=\"2 1 []\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://codame.substack.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Sign Up</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://codame.com/pages/support-art-tech\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Support</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1><code><strong>PROJECTS <br /><br /><img src=\"/uploaded_images/ezgif.com-optimize_2.gif\" alt=\"\" /><br /></strong></code></h1>\r\n<p>Shine brighter by supporting innovation in fashion - <a href=\"https://www.hackster.io/conceptcindy/fun-pants-i-invite-individuals-to-step-into-their-own-light-09f79b\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">vote for FUN PANTS on Hackster.io today</a> and help us revolutionize the way we express ourselves through clothing. <strong>Fun Pants </strong>is interactive fashion by <a href=\"http://codame.com/artists/cindy-clark\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">ConceptCindy</a> for the <a href=\"https://www.hackster.io/contests/sustainablefashion\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Hackster FashionTech Design Challange 2023</a>.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\r\n<figure><source srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3ab2e89e-33f3-41c3-8a6b-456b8c9d2edb_600x338.gif 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3ab2e89e-33f3-41c3-8a6b-456b8c9d2edb_600x338.gif 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3ab2e89e-33f3-41c3-8a6b-456b8c9d2edb_600x338.gif 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3ab2e89e-33f3-41c3-8a6b-456b8c9d2edb_600x338.gif 1456w\" type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"100vw\" />\r\n<div class=\"image2-inset\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1><code><strong>EVENTS </strong></code></h1>\r\n<div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\r\n<figure><source srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F45211919-1a52-44e2-ac09-3160f57da8fe_2480x1467.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F45211919-1a52-44e2-ac09-3160f57da8fe_2480x1467.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F45211919-1a52-44e2-ac09-3160f57da8fe_2480x1467.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F45211919-1a52-44e2-ac09-3160f57da8fe_2480x1467.jpeg 1456w\" type=\"image/webp\" sizes=\"100vw\" />\r\n<div class=\"image2-inset\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F517d1b29-bb6d-49df-952a-fdb993759820_1650x1291.png\" alt=\"ButtonWeavers-com-Offline-Edition-DWebCamp2023\" /></p>\r\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><a href=\"https://dwebcamp2023.sched.com/event/1Nu0K/bringing-characters-you-love-to-life-with-composable-gaming\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Bring Characters You Love To Life With Composable Gaming</a> workshop by <a href=\"http://codame.com/artists/jordan-gray\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Jordan Gray </a>is being held Friday, June 23 at <a href=\"http://dwebcamp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">#DWebCamp2023</a> at Camp Navarro, CA. This workshop takes a break from utility to unleash your creative imagination with play.</p>\r\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h1 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><code><strong>OPPORTUNITIES</strong><code> <br /><br /></code></code></h1>\r\n<pre data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><img style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\" src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F71735ebf-7fd0-473a-b06d-d160721e8952_1404x534.png\" alt=\"\" />&nbsp;</pre>\r\n<div class=\"captioned-image-container\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>OPEN CALL Foundation! Theme: Abstraction: Beyond Boundaries Curated by <a class=\"css-4rbku5 css-18t94o4 css-901oao css-16my406 r-1cvl2hr r-1loqt21 r-poiln3 r-bcqeeo r-qvutc0\" href=\"https://twitter.com/oneo2studio\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">@Oneo2studio</a> and <a class=\"css-4rbku5 css-18t94o4 css-901oao css-16my406 r-1cvl2hr r-1loqt21 r-poiln3 r-bcqeeo r-qvutc0\" href=\"https://twitter.com/ParinHeidari\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">@ParinHeidari</a>. Deadline: June 25th, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ParinHeidari/status/1671266060631445504\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">submit on Twitter</a>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F137feab2-7c72-47b1-bf56-7faa5e30488f_3444x1226.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">ANTIDOTE festival brings together the best of the best in the Web3, featuring industry-leading panelists, prolific artists, influential figures, groundbreaking innovators, and live performances. This open call is to curate a room with a lot of amazing art! <a href=\"https://twitter.com/objktcom/status/1671163991085948935\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Send us your best Tezos work</a> - old or new - and tell us what it is an antidote for.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><!-- pagebreak -->&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h1><code><strong>SPONSORS&nbsp;</strong></code></h1>\r\n<p>Be recognized as a visionary supporter of CODAME.&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/support-art-tech\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Sponsor the ART+TECH Newsletter</a>!</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>Thanks for joining us! See you in a week &amp; don&rsquo;t forget to submit your exciting Interviews, Projects, Events, Workshops, and Call For Proposals to the CODAME ART+TECH Newsletter&hellip;&nbsp;<a href=\"/projects/art-tech-newsletter\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">right here</a>!</p>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Subscribe</h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe style=\"border-style: solid; border-color: #eeeeee; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-color: white;\" src=\"https://codame.substack.com/embed\" width=\"480\" height=\"320\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '0'),
(79, 'The Future of CODAME', 'the-future-of-codame', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/the-future-of-codame.jpeg', '<p><strong>Celebrating Humanity and ART+TECH around the world</strong></p>\r\n<p>It is with great excitement and profound gratitude that we share our vision for the future of our beloved organization. CODAME has made significant progress since its inception as a local art and technology community in San Francisco. CODAME has come a long way since its foggy rooftop first ART+TECH Festival in 2010. Today, it has evolved into a movement that thrives at the vibrant crossroads of art and technology worldwide. We warmly invite you to be part of this exciting evolution as we continue to spark innovation through inspiring experiences. This post discusses the strategic pillars shaping CODAME\'s future in the coming year:</p>\r\n<p><strong>Expand Internationally</strong></p>\r\n<p>Strengthening Connections around the World through ART+TECH.</p>\r\n<p>In a world where conflicts, divisions, and inequalities often dominate the headlines, we wholeheartedly believe in the incredible ability of art to unite us. Art brings people together regardless of where you\'re from, what you believe in, or the language you speak.</p>\r\n<p>At CODAME, our core mission has always been connecting people, ideas, and cultures. Our co-founder, Bruno Fonzi, originally from Italy, lived in France, England, Australia, and Germany before moving to San Francisco 14 years ago when CODAME was born. His international perspective has inspired us to take CODAME\'s worldwide presence to new heights. Bruno is working on an exciting project in Milan, further strengthening our global connections and collaborations.</p>\r\n<p>We are thrilled to announce our commitment to expanding CODAME\'s footprint outside the US. We aim to forge a stronger connection between the art and tech communities around the globe. CODAME presence in Europe is the starting point to facilitate stronger cross-cultural collaborations, allowing artists, technologists, and innovators from diverse corners of the world to converge, share their unique insights, and collaborate on groundbreaking art and tech projects. This international outreach will enrich our community and advance our mission to explore the boundless energy of collaborations, discoveries, and explorations at the nexus of art and technology.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Focusing on People</strong></p>\r\n<p>Recognizing Our Community, the Artists and Volunteers.</p>\r\n<p>In the era of artificial intelligence and automation, it is crucial to acknowledge that while technology is a potent force, it is the people behind it who shape the course of our world. CODAME has always centered around the exceptional individuals who bring our events and projects to life. From the awe-inspiring artists who craft captivating installations to the devoted volunteers who tirelessly support our initiatives, our community is the lifeblood of CODAME.</p>\r\n<p>In the forthcoming year, our commitment is to place a well-deserved spotlight on the outstanding individuals who embody the essence of CODAME. We will extend our support and offer our artists and volunteers greater recognition. We aspire to empower them to continue to push the boundaries of art and technology. By focusing on people, we can continue nurturing a dynamic, inclusive community that thrives on creativity, collaboration, and innovation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Our co-founder, Jordan Gray, exemplifies this ethos, whose Qigong journey since his certification in 2015 has deeply influenced CODAME\'s playful and personal approach. If you are in San Francisco, we encourage you to connect with Jordan and catch a glimpse of this spirit with Jordan\'s free&nbsp;<a href=\"/events/goose-gong\" rel=\"\">Qigong sessions</a>&nbsp;at Sue Bierman Park every Saturday at 10:00 a.m.</p>\r\n<p><strong>The ART+TECH Festival</strong></p>\r\n<p>The Essence of Creativity, Innovation, and Humanity around the world.</p>\r\n<p>One of the highlights of the CODAME calendar is our ART+TECH Festival. It has consistently been a beacon of creativity and a platform for art and technology to design unforgettable, inspiring experiences. We are delighted to unveil a new dimension of the ART+TECH Festival in the upcoming year, connecting people around the world.</p>\r\n<p>Our next ART+TECH Festival will not only feature awe-inspiring art installations and cutting-edge tech exhibits but will also serve as a global rendezvous for our community. It will be a space where artists, technologists, and enthusiasts from every corner of the world can come together to celebrate the profound impact of human creativity and the limitless possibilities that await at the intersection of art and technology.</p>\r\n<p>The future of CODAME ART+TECH is bursting with promise and potential. Our commitment to expanding our horizons, celebrating our incredible community members, and hosting groundbreaking events like the ART+TECH Festival remains unwavering.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Join us!</strong></p>\r\n<p>As a Volunteer, Sponsor, or Artist.</p>\r\n<p>We wholeheartedly invite you to join us on this exhilarating journey as we build bridges, empower our community, and inspire the world through the enchanting fusion of art and technology.</p>\r\n<p>If you are in Milan, San Francisco, or anywhere else in the world, and as excited as we are about the future of CODAME, now\'s the perfect moment to dive in more deeply as a volunteer, artist, or sponsor! Share your triumphs, challenges, and thoughts on our evolving direction. We\'re seeking collaborators, old and new, who share our passion for art, technology, and community building.</p>\r\n<p>Please get in touch with us to contribute your skills as a&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/call-for-volunteers\" rel=\"\">volunteer</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://codame.com/pages/support-art-tech\" rel=\"\">sponsorship</a>&nbsp;as an organization, or enthusiasm as an&nbsp;<a href=\"http://codame.com/pages/call-for-proposals\" rel=\"\">artist</a>. Together, we will craft the future of CODAME and continue to push the boundaries of what is possible in the captivating realm of art and technology.</p>\r\n<p>With gratitude and excitement,</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"/artists/bruno-fonzi\" rel=\"\">Bruno Fonzi</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"/artists/jordan-gray\" rel=\"\">Jordan Gray</a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Co-Founders of&nbsp;<a href=\"http://codame.com/\" rel=\"\">CODAME</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div><hr /></div>\r\n<p>Hyperlinks mentioned in this post:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><a href=\"/pages/call-for-volunteers\" rel=\"\">Call for Volunteers</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://codame.com/pages/support-art-tech\" rel=\"\">Support ART+TECH</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://codame.com/pages/call-for-proposals\" rel=\"\">Call for Artist Proposals</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><a href=\"/events/goose-gong\" rel=\"\">Qigong sessions</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<p><a href=\"/projects/phracktography\" rel=\"\">Phracktography</a></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `pages` (`id`, `name`, `slug`, `pic`, `description`, `old_url`, `hidden`) VALUES
(80, 'The Essence of the next CODAME ART+TECH Festival', 'the-essence-of-the-next-codame-art-tech-festival', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/discover-the-essence-of-the-next-codame-art-tech-festival.gif', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;\">As we eagerly prepare for the upcoming edition of the CODAME ART+TECH Festival, we are thrilled to unveil the theme that will guide our creative journey: Essence.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Essence encapsulates the heart of what we aim to explore and celebrate&mdash;a profound examination of the core, the soul, and the quintessence of the dynamic relationship between art and technology. As we embrace the theme of Essence for this year\'s ART+TECH Festival, we find a powerful connection to our three main additional focuses we <a href=\"/pages/the-future-of-codame\">recently announced at CODAME</a>: Celebrating Humanity and ART+TECH around the world.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">We celebrate the Essence of human creativity and collaboration by placing People at the forefront of our mission. Our global community, stretching across continents, embodies the international spirit that drives us to connect, learn, and create together. Expanding Internationally, as we aim to bridge geographical divides and build a more interconnected world of art and technology. Essence reflects our commitment to bringing diverse perspectives and cultures together to enrich our creative landscape.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In the fusion of these pillars, we discover the Essence of CODAME. This community thrives on the passion, innovation, and collaboration of people from all walks of life, irrespective of where they call home. Together, we will explore the Essence of art, technology, and the human experience at the upcoming festival, forging connections that transcend borders and celebrating the universal spirit of creativity that unites us all.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Essence reminds us that at the heart of every innovation, creative endeavor, and connection we make, a fundamental shared human experience transcends borders and cultures. As you reflect on what essence means to you, how would you express essence?</p>\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Join Us in Celebrating Essence&nbsp;</strong></h2>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"803\" height=\"803\" /></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The CODAME ART+TECH Festival has always allowed artists to express themselves uniquely and imaginatively. Essence is an invitation to artists to examine their work at its core, to peel back the layers and reveal the Essence of their creative process. Essence is an exploration of the raw, the elemental, and the authentic.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Our theme invites artists, technologists, and innovators to embark on a creative journey that transcends boundaries. It challenges us to strip away the superfluous and focus on what truly matters. Essence asks: What is the Essence of a brushstroke, a line of code, or a musical note? How do these elements combine to create art that reflects and reshapes our world?&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Call for Artists&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><img src=\"/uploaded_images/11.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Are you an artist with a vision that pushes the boundaries of art and technology? We invite artists worldwide to join us in celebrating the Essence theme at our next ART+TECH Festival. Whether it\'s an interactive installation, a multimedia performance, or a groundbreaking tech-art concept, we\'re eager to see your creativity shine. Share your unique perspective and inspire others; submit your project proposals today and be a part of the future of art and technology! <a href=\"/pages/call-for-proposals\">https://codame.com/pages/call-for-proposals</a></p>\r\n<h2>Call for Volunteers&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><img src=\"/uploaded_images/121.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>It&rsquo;s a fun and enriching experience as you learn new skills and pass your knowledge on to others. You&rsquo;ll meet like-minded people, make friends, and build a network of people from all backgrounds who share a common passion for ART+TECH.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><a href=\"/pages/call-for-volunteers\">Apply</a> to be part of the magic! We&rsquo;re looking for outstanding volunteers to support our ART+TECH initiatives.&nbsp;<a href=\"/pages/call-for-volunteers\">https://codame.com/pages/call-for-volunteers</a></p>\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Call for Partners</h2>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"/uploaded_images/17.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"800\" height=\"800\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Host the ART+TECH Festival in Your City&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We invite individuals, venues, and organizations worldwide who share our passion for art, technology, and community to host the CODAME ART+TECH Festival in your city. By bringing this global celebration to your local community, you\'ll have the opportunity to showcase your region\'s incredible talent and innovation while becoming part of our international network of creativity and collaboration. If you\'re interested in joining us on this exciting journey and becoming a festival host, please don\'t hesitate to contact us.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Together, we can amplify the impact of art and technology on a global scale and create a unique experience for your city. Contact us today to explore the possibilities! <a href=\"/pages/support-art-tech\">https://codame.com/pages/support-art-tech</a></p>\r\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Stay Tuned for More</h2>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong><img src=\"/uploaded_images/14.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"797\" height=\"797\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">In the coming months, we will be sharing updates, calls for proposals, and exciting developments as we prepare for the festival. We look forward to witnessing how our community interprets and expresses the Essence of ART+TECH.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Thank you for being a part of the CODAME family, and we can\'t wait to explore the Essence of art and technology with you at the upcoming festival.</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">With anticipation and creativity,</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">The CODAME Team&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '', '0');
