(263, 'Spaces Gallery', 'spaces-gallery', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Part of the 10th annual <a href=\"/events/art-tech-festival-2020-joynt\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME ART+TECH Festival</a> (included in the</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\">Festival Pass and All Access Pass</a>&nbsp;)</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"-en-clipboard: true;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Spaces3.0 is building a 3D webspace that allows anyone to search and find 3D content on the web starting off with 3D art.</span></div>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><!--?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?--></p>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">Spaces i</span><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">nteractive 3D art</span> <span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">gallery will be featuring 3D profiles of this year\'s CODAME Art+Tech Festival Artists.</span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.tickettailor.com/events/codame/442122/#ticket_selection\" target=\"_blank\"><img style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-family: Asap, helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; color: #00a4a7; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"/uploaded_images/button_(6).png\" alt=\"CODAME ART+TECH Get Tickets Button\" /></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://muse.place/khoparzi\" target=\"_blank\">Abhinay - https://muse.place/khoparzi</a><br /> <a href=\"https://muse.place/alexandershortt\" target=\"_blank\">Alex (Spaces) - https://muse.place/alexandershortt</a><br /> <a href=\"https://muse.place/empowa\" target=\"_blank\">Ash Herr - https://muse.place/empowa</a><br /> <a href=\"https://muse.place/asyncart\" target=\"_blank\">Async Art - https://muse.place/asyncart</a><br /> <a href=\"https://muse.place/bruno\" target=\"_blank\">B