(288, 'Regalia or Chromology ðŸ¤”', 'regalia-or-chromology', '<p>Made with Regalia (or Chromology) by Fabin Rasheed, hosted in async.art</p>', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/regalia-or-chromology.png', '', 'https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/6456508792435698253940879432024', 'fabin-rasheed', '', '0', '1623364726', 'https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/64565087924356982539408794320246414468607019910359975833310188526433562787841', '', '', 'nft'),
(289, 'DOOMSLUG', 'doomslug', '<p>NEAR relies on its own variant of BFT consensus, known as DOOMSLUG. It facilitates sub-second block production and recovers the network from malicious or unresponsive validators. ðŸ’ªðŸ˜ŽðŸ’¨ DOOMSLUG is also a mascot that accompanies Spensa Nightshade in Skyward. She\'s known to replicate nearly any sound she hears. ðŸŒðŸŽ¶ DOOMSLUG was first drawn on a 4x4 plot of pixelparty.pixeldapps.co. This design was captured by the original artist and is being immortalized as the CODAME genesis NFT on Mintbase; as an ode to the beauty of technology! ðŸŽ¨ðŸ‘©&zwj;ðŸ’»ðŸ‘¾</p>', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/doomslug.png', '', 'https://www.mintbase.io/thing/8Y2mQRT7B4t0m_qgaqvdry7XHbTEhIbDjnSdWKTFxw0:codame.mintbase1.near', 'jordan-gray', '', '0', '1625532310', 'https://codame.threadless.com/designs/doomslug-starpause', 'mintbase', '', 'nft'),
(290, 'Trench 1.1', 'trench-1-1', '<p>Trench is set in a digitally simulated space resembling an abstracted oceanic environment not unlike the Mariana Trench. While diving deeper within the simulation, the participant approach&rsquo;s various CGI marine-like objects, which will trigger natural and glitched phenomena that alter the digital experience. Fu&rsquo;s work draws parallels between the physical, virtual, metaphysical, and multi-dimensional, setting the viewer in a liminal space at the threshold of each in what Turner called &ldquo;a period of scrutiny for central values and axioms.&rdquo; Within the digital space created by Snow Yunxue Fu, we are offered an encounter to reflect on our response to the simultaneously beautiful and overwhelming artifice of the techno-sublime.</p>', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/trench-1-1.jpg', '', 'https://www.mintbase.io/thing/mvGRvEbA_tA9vw3wGjDm_I-P5nDYL8z5qVY0dT6yhZc:codame.mintbase1.near', 'snow-yunxue-fu', '', '0', '1622649638', 'https://www.mintbase.io/thing/mvGRvEbA_tA9vw3wGjDm_I-P5nDYL8z5qVY0dT6yhZc:codame.mintbase1.near', 'mintbase', '', 'nft'),
(291, 'Magical Roses', 'magical-roses', '<p>Magical roses only exist in hyperreality, suspended somewhere in the space between digital and physical, 2D and 3D. The lens flare and glitter they give off are more than just visual effects, they use the lighting of the sparkles to traverse through dimensions. Although beautiful, it is a rare flower. While wandering the metaverse, keep an eye out for anything exceptionally dazzling &ndash; It might be magical.</p>', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/magical-roses.gif', '', 'https://www.mintbase.io/thing/bQ4iQw6IOMELIrsmd4mAWCoEpYv0WRjTxu9R_EZ2Cs4:codame.mintbase1.near', 'crystal-glass', '', '0', '1622651678', 'https://www.mintbase.io/thing/bQ4iQw6IOMELIrsmd4mAWCoEpYv0WRjTxu9R_EZ2Cs4:codame.mintbase1.near', 'mintbase', '', 'nft'),
