(298, 'PENSk9o', 'pensk9o', '<p><a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: transparent; color: #039be5; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;\" href=\"https://hydra.ojack.xyz/?\" target=\"_blank\">staRpauSe remix</a>&nbsp;of a hydra script by&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: transparent; color: #039be5; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;\" href=\"/artists/flor-de-fuego\" target=\"_blank\">Flor De Fuego</a>. Flor and&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: transparent; color: #039be5; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;\" href=\"/artists/naoto-hieda\" target=\"_blank\">Naoto Hieda</a>&nbsp;will talk about their distanced collaboration&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: transparent; color: #039be5; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;\" href=\"/events/glitch-me-introduction\" target=\"_blank\">Glitch.me on Fri 12/18</a>!</p>\r\n<p>Minted my k9d with permission of Flor during the monthly&nbsp;<a style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: transparent; color: #039be5; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; text-decoration-line: none; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis;\" href=\"/events/happy-hour-on-discord\" target=\"_blank\">CODAME Happy Hour on Discord</a>.</p>', 'http://codame.dreamhosters.com/uploaded_images/pensk9o.png', '', '', '', '', '0', '1623365114', 'https://opensea.io/assets/0x495f947276749ce646f68ac8c248420045cb7b5e/64565087924356982539408794320246414468607019910359975833310188529732097671169', '', '', 'nft'),
